data.chText: 不知道；没意识到；未察觉
data.enText: not knowing or realizing that sth is happening or that sth exists

data.chText: 他对整件事情一无所知。
data.enText: He was completely unaware of the whole affair.
She was unaware that I could see her.

simple_means.memory_skill: un 不 + aware 意识到的 → 不知道的

example: unaware of the danger they were in
the most unaware person I've known

value.def: If you are unaware of something, you do not know about it.

example.ex: Many people are unaware of just how much food and drink they consume...
example.tran: 许多人并不知道他们究竟消耗掉了多少食品和饮料。

example.ex: She was unaware that she was being filmed.
example.tran: 她不知道有人在拍摄她。

gramarinfo.label: v-link ADJ, usu ADJ <l>of</l> n, ADJ that

value.tran: 不知道的；不晓得的；未注意到的

partsOfSpeech.dec: a 表加强 + ware 注视 → 一直注视 → 意识到的
be 使… + ware 注视 → 睁大眼睛注视 → 谨防
un 不 + aware 意识到的 → 不知道的
war〔e〕注视 + y 多…的，有…的 → 时刻注视的 → 警惕的
